element.name: Eaglais agus Túr by Windsockers, Traditional Cache (1.5/1)

long-description.p: This cache is located in the ruins of the Baldungan church and tower, located somewhere between Rush, Lusk, Loughshinny, and Skerries in Fingal (appproximately 20 miles north of Dublin). All that remains of the Church are the outer walls of the church, and the tower. Unfortunately access to the tower is closed off. There is a small cemetary around the castle, which is still in use.

A nice place with a great view, this is a nice location off the beaten track along the coast of Ireland. The cache itself (a small tablock box) should not be too hard to find, so when you're in the neighbourhood, make sure to visit!
